  "3302600": {
    "name": "Itty Bitty Little Kitties",
    "steam_appid": 3302600,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Click to find the kittens.</strong> Welcome to a world of wonders and adorable little kittens.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302600/extras/af3b5269af5929157213ee9ac31bae73.avif?t=1750194031\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302600/extras_big/af3b5269af5929157213ee9ac31bae73.avif?t=1750194031 width=800 height=166 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > In this hidden object game, you’ll embark on a journey through beautiful, magical forest scenes, each filled with charming little kittens waiting to be found.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s a world where each kitty’s personality and unique traits are revealed to you as you progress through each level.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302600/extras/50de9aa245ba419997948b49f761f7f8.poster.avif?t=1750194031\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302600/extras/50de9aa245ba419997948b49f761f7f8.webm?t=1750194031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302600/extras/50de9aa245ba419997948b49f761f7f8.mp4?t=1750194031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Key Features:</u></strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Adorable Kittens</strong>: Discover the exquisitely tiny but cute little kittens, each uniquely created in various art styles ranging from stylized to realistic to 3D cartoon types.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302600/extras/4ddb0c4e29b3851db68754ffbe623174.avif?t=1750194031\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302600/extras_big/4ddb0c4e29b3851db68754ffbe623174.avif?t=1750194031 width=800 height=166 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Relaxing Music</strong>: Enjoy beautiful, calming music that enhances your search and makes the experience even more enjoyable.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Untimed Gameplay</strong>: Sometimes it's nice to relax. Here you can take your time and enjoy the challenge without the pressure of a ticking clock.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Magical Forest Scenes</strong>: Explore stunning forest environments that evoke a sense of wonder and fantasy.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302600/extras/c8a8c380cfe66e21acd82c8aef45c975.poster.avif?t=1750194031\" width=800 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302600/extras/c8a8c380cfe66e21acd82c8aef45c975.webm?t=1750194031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302600/extras/c8a8c380cfe66e21acd82c8aef45c975.mp4?t=1750194031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Levels and Bonus Content</strong>: Play through six enchanting scenes and unlock a <i>big</i> special bonus level.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hidden Kitties:</strong> Find over 1100 kittens hidden throughout seven stunning scenes. Each kitten is accompanied by a photo and usually a fun fact about their personality and traits.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Automatic Saving</strong>: Your progress is saved automatically to the cloud, so you can always pick up right where you left off on any PC.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you’re a cat lover, or a fan of hidden object games, or just someone looking for a relaxing break, try this game.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FAQs</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>What happens if I can’t find all the kittens in a level?</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don’t worry! You can take your time to find all the kittens because the game is designed to be relaxing and untimed, so there’s no rush. If you need a break, your progress will be saved automatically, allowing you to pick up where you left off.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But if you’re really stuck, you can use a hint, which is available once every two minutes.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Should I play the Demo?</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Yes, because the demo has extra content. It has two unique levels and 220 cute little kittens to be found.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Why do I hear kittens meowing sometimes while playing the game?</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Occasionally as your mouse cursor hovers over a hidden kitten, she will meow to give you an idea of her location to help you in the game.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302600/extras/897c50b97b804532c5f74d3b48b4ebb8.avif?t=1750194031\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302600/extras_big/897c50b97b804532c5f74d3b48b4ebb8.avif?t=1750194031 width=800 height=166 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302600/extras/c19bf18c6eb7f8e4193e00467c4e00a3.avif?t=1750194031\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302600/extras_big/c19bf18c6eb7f8e4193e00467c4e00a3.avif?t=1750194031 width=800 height=77 /></span></p>",
